1. Module Purpose

The Interest Engine is the financial calculation core of the platform.

Every Girvi transaction, payment, renewal, redemption, report, compliance document, and customer statement depends on this module.

The module is responsible for:

* Simple Interest Calculation
* Katmiti Interest Calculation
* Daily Interest Calculation
* Overdue Penalty Calculation
* Minimum Billing Rule Enforcement
* Interest Ledger Management
* Future Interest Forecasting
* Interest Recalculation
* RBI Compliance
* Financial Audit Trail

