6. Core Business Rules

BR-INT-001

Interest can never be negative.

BR-INT-002

Historical calculations are immutable.

BR-INT-003

Interest rate changes affect future accrual only.

BR-INT-004

Katmiti payments cover interest first.

BR-INT-005

Penalty interest displayed separately.

BR-INT-006

Interest ledger cannot be deleted.

BR-INT-007

Every calculation must be auditable.

BR-INT-008

Calculation engine runs server-side.

