11. Minimum Billing Engine

Purpose

Prevent early settlement abuse.

⸻

Rule

Settlement between:

Day 1
Day 15

Requires:

Minimum One Month Interest

⸻

Formula

Minimum\ Charge = One\ Full\ Month\ Interest

⸻

Configuration

Tenant configurable.

⸻

12. Overdue Penalty Engine

Trigger

Due date crossed.

⸻

Formula

Penalty = Outstanding \times Penalty\ Rate \times \frac{Overdue\ Days}{365}

⸻

Inputs

Outstanding Principal
Penalty Rate
Overdue Days

⸻

Rules

Separate Ledger

Penalty never merged into regular interest.

⸻

Separate Display

Visible in all reports.

⸻

